item.description:
One Life Remaining: Season 1 Episode 1 (halo machinima)
HALO. Pilot episode of a new Halo 3 machinima series by Jon CJG, creator, writer and director of Arby 'n' the Chief. The series follows a retro gamer and high school student named Anthony Heitzmann, starting with his graduation, and will continue to follow him as he gradually puts his terrible school years and hometown behind him and moves out into the big city with a degree in computer sciences under his belt with Chad Mueller, his constantly inebriated and physically as well as mentally unappealing roommate. However it is through Chad that Anthony grows up, gets hired and fired from various game developers and even meets the girl of his dreams. The series begins with Anthony's graduation, and to celebrate, his mother Deborah decides to take him out to dinner and to Anthony's disappointment, the waitress happens to be his high school's "alpha-tramp".
